title: Stuart Binny, Ajinkya Rahane slog it out at Team India practice ahead of 3rd T20
text: Having warmed the benches in India's two back-to-back defeats, Ajinkya Rahane and Stuart Binny may get a look-in for the third and final T20 match here tomorrow as the two players slogged it out at India's practice session ahead of the dead rubber. Â»
